meaningMnemonic: You already learned that the word 時期 means "time period," so when you add <kanji>furthermore</kanji> and <kanji>early</kanji> to that, it means that something happened ahead of time. It means <vocabulary>premature</vocabulary>.
readingMnemonic: This is a jukugo word that uses the on'yomi readings of the kanji. You should be able to read this on your own.
